---
title: Mushroom & Soy Ramen with Fried Onions
description: Our chefs are obsessed with ramen—and no, we don’t mean the instant variety. We’re talking about that soul-stirring combination of rich miso broth, soy-ginger mushrooms, and a tangle of chewy noodles. For this veggie-centric version, each bowl is topped off with crispy onions, scallion greens, and as much (or little!) Sriracha as your heart desires. If you weren’t a hopeless ramen-tic yet, this will make you one.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/612f9ce9c334d0481161d824-80afa57f.jpg
